      <!-- Vegan & Halal Guide CTA -->
      <aside class="section aside-panel" aria-labelledby="guide-cta-heading">
        <h2 id="guide-cta-heading">üå± Korean Cuisine for Every Diet</h2>
        <p>
          Enjoy Korean food adapted for diverse dietary needs including vegan, halal, and gluten-free.
          Choose vegan or halal-certified jang products, and substitute stock with vegetable broth or shiitake mushroom water.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Use vegan-certified doenjang and gochujang</li>
          <li>Create deep flavors with vegetable or shiitake mushroom broth</li>
          <li>Replace sesame oil with perilla oil or grapeseed oil</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="button tertiary" href="guides/vegan-halal.html">Read Full Guide ‚Üí</a>
